                            been
                            ruled
                            out
                            for Tuesday's contest against the Magic. It marks George's second
                            straight
                            absence,
                            as he also missed Monday's game against the Bucks due to a sore
                            foot.
                            Forward
                            Marcus
                            Morris Sr., guard Reggie Jackson, and guard Luke Kennard scored
                            20-plus
                            points
                            with
                            at least four triples without George in the picture against
                            Milwaukee.
                            The
                            Magic
