                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title newsTitle">De'Andre Hunter Ruled Out Sunday</h5>
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        <p class="card-text">Atlanta Hawks forward De'Andre Hunter (knee) will
                            not
                            play
                            Sunday against the Denver Nuggets. Hunter recently returned from a
                            lengthy
                            knee
                            injury and is experiencing knee soreness, missing the past two
                            games. It
                            is
                            possible Hunter may have returned too soon which made his knee flare
                            up.
                            Regardless, Hunter's absence should lead to another start for Tony
                            Snell
                            and
                            more minutes for Bogdan Bogdanovic, Danilo Gallinari and Kevin
                            Huerter.
                            John
                            Collins is also a big winner here and should be a popular DFS target
                            in
                            this
                            one.
                        </p>
                    </blockquote>

                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary news-btn">View Full Story</a>
                </div>
            </div>
